# React RHF, table, a11y & export lint (portable)

**Canonical:** `docs/dev/rules/react-rhf-and-table-lint.md`  
**Checklist:** `docs/dev/rules/react-lint-verification-checklist.md`  
**Effects / Link:** `docs/dev/rules/react-effects-patterns.md`

## Rules (CI errors)

| Rule | Fix |
|------|-----|
| `react-hooks/incompatible-library` (RHF) | `useWatch({ control, name })` — never `form.watch()` in JSX or hooks |
| `react-hooks/incompatible-library` (table) | `eslint-disable-next-line` above `useReactTable` only |
| `import/no-anonymous-default-export` | `const x = {...}; export default x` |
| `jsx-a11y/role-supports-aria-props` | `role="combobox"` + `aria-controls` + `role="listbox"` on list |

## Before done

```bash
cd web-admin && npx eslint . --quiet && npx tsc --noEmit
```

**Copy to other projects:** adjust `globs` above to your app folder (e.g. `src/**`).
